quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  27,77,"Ne toto Ikurani ino ni obulunjifu nende tsimbabaasi khubalia abasuubila."
  27,78,"Toto Nyasaye alikhalaka eshina hakari wabu khukhukhalaka eshina khukhwe, naye niye Owamani, Omumanyi muno."
  27,79,"Kho wisiche Nyasaye, toto ewe oli khubwatoto bulolekha."
  27,80,"Toto ewe shonyala okhukhola abafu bawulile omulango tawe, nohomba okhole abekala amarwi bawulila tawe olwa bakalukhananga nibeetsila."
  27,81,"Nohomba shonyala okhulunjisia abawofu okhurula mubukori bwabu tawe, ne sholaulilisia tsinyaali tsiefu tawe halali balia abatsisuubiranga, nabo naabasalamu."
  27,82,"Ne olwa likhuwa lilibarulila, khulibarusilia isolo okhurula mwiloba ibalomalomie mbu toto abandu bakhaya okhusuubila tsinyaali tsiefu."
  27,83,"Ne inyanga yakhulikhung’asia okhurula mubuli Abandu omukanda kwa balia abayingasinjia ebimanyisio biefu, ne baliemibwa ebituche ebituche."
  27,84,"Okhula shingala baliula, mana (Nyasaye) aboole mbu: “Koo, enywe mwakatsula ebimanyisio bianje nimulabimanyile obulayi tawe, nohomba nishina shiamwakholanga?”"
  27,85,"Mana likhuwa nilibakwila khumabii kabakhola, ne baliwulela tsi."
  27,86,"Koo, shibalolangakhwo mbu efwe khwakhola eshilo okhuba shiokhwihotselesiamwo, ne eshitere okhubakhonya okhulola? Toto mu ako kalimwo ameeko khubandu basuubilanga."
  27,87,"Ne inyanga yolwika lulifurwamwo, mana bibeyebeye bioosi ebili mwikulu nende khushialo halali ulia wa Nyasaye alichama. Ne boosi bakhamwitsile nibali abateshele."
  27,88,"Ne olilola efikulu nopara mbu fiemele, nafio khufibura shinga amaleesi. Nibo obwiranyi bwa Nyasaye, owakasia obulayi buli eshindu. Toto ye amanyile muno akamukholanga."